"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Interactive planning</span><h2>See everything laid out on the map</h2><p>Use the live map to lock in nearby options, preview ratings, and save time hopping between neighborhoods.</p></div><div class=\"map-grid\"><div class=\"map-panel\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div style=\"min-height:320px;background:#f3f4f6\"></div><!--/$--></div><div class=\"map-sidebar\"><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Quick filters</h3><div class=\"map-chip-grid\"><button type=\"button\"><span>Dog Park</span><small>21</small></button></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Highest-rated nearby</h3><div class=\"mini-park-list\"><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Petco Dog Training</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>5.0</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Wild Child Play Company</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>5.0</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>K9 Resorts Luxury Pet Hotel Cherry Hill</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.9</strong></div></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card muted\"><p>Tip: tap any map marker to open directions, amenities, and current open hours.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"planning-essentials\" class=\"planning-essentials-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Visit toolkit</span><h2>Plan the perfect dog outing in <!-- -->Cherry Hill Township</h2><p>Borrow best practices from local trainers, rangers, and experienced pet parents.</p></div><div class=\"planning-grid\"><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h3>Peak &amp; quiet windows</h3><ul><li>6–9 AM: high energy social hour</li><li>10 AM–3 PM weekdays: calm training-friendly window</li><li>After 4 PM: sunset crowd + cooler temps</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-backpack\"></i></div><h3>Essentials checklist</h3><ul><li>Leash + harness for entry/exit control</li><li>Collapsible water bowl and fresh water</li><li>Plenty of waste bags and high-value treats</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-shield-check\"></i></div><h3>Local regulations</h3><ul><li>Keep proof of vaccinations or city license handy</li><li>Voice control required in most off-leash zones</li><li>Limit three dogs per handler in public parks</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-heart\"></i></div><h3>Community etiquette</h3><ul><li>Scan the park before entering and remove prong collars</li><li>Monitor play styles and intervene early</li><li>Share shaded space and refill water when you&#x27;re done</li></ul></article></div></div></section><section id=\"owner-cta\" class=\"owner-cta-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Partner with us</span><h2>Feature your Cherry Hill Township dog park</h2><p>Upgrade to a featured listing, share live availability, or pitch a new indoor concept. Our team drives qualified local pet parents every week.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\" style=\"margin-top:24px\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List a property</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Contact the team</a></div></div></section><section id=\"park-directory\" class=\"park-directory-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">City directory</span><h2>All dog parks in <!-- -->Cherry Hill Township</h2><p>Filter-ready cards with ratings, amenities, and quick actions. Use the chips to jump between sections.</p></div><div class=\"category-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\">Dog Park</button></div><div id=\"dog-park-parks\" class=\"directory-category\"><div class=\"directory-header\"><div><h3>Dog Park<!-- -->s<!-- --> in <!-- -->Cherry Hill Township</h3><p>21<!-- --> locations ·<!-- --> <!-- -->4.4<!-- --> <!-- -->average rating</p></div><span class=\"directory-count\">21</span></div><div class=\"directory-grid\"><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/all-paws-rock-llc\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">All Paws Rock, LLC</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 9:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Cherry Hill Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">If you&#x27;re looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [Cherry Hill Township](/cities/cherry-hill-township-nj), look no further than All Paws Rock, LLC. This vibrant community destination has earned a reputation as the &quot;place to be&quot; for local pet parents who want more than just a walk—they want a meetup. Boasting a solid 4.7-star rating from 75 reviews, the park radiates a welcoming energy where tails never stop wagging and neighbors become friends. Whether you&#x27;re there for a quick playdate or a long afternoon of socializing, the atmosphere is always buzzing with positivity.\n\nAt All Paws Rock, LLC, the focus is on connection. The layout encourages interaction, making it easy for pups to find playmates while owners chat on the sidelines. It’s not just a facility; it’s a social pillar of the Cherry Hill Township scene, offering a safe, clean, and joyous environment where every visitor feels like a VIP. For a fun, friendly, and community-centered experience, this spot is a local favorite.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](http://www.allpawsrock.com/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/camp-bow-wow-cherry-hill\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Camp Bow Wow Cherry Hill</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 6:30 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Cherry Hill Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">For years, Camp Bow Wow Cherry Hill has served as a steadfast anchor of the [Cherry Hill Township](/cities/cherry-hill-township-nj) community, earning its place as a beloved local institution. With a history of serving generations of tail-waggers, this location carries a sense of established trust and neighborhood pride that you can&#x27;t manufacture. Documented by 337 reviews and a 4.8-star legacy, it stands as a testament to the town&#x27;s enduring commitment to its animal residents.\n\nStepping into Camp Bow Wow Cherry Hill feels like visiting an old friend. The facility balances traditional park values with modern maintenance standards, ensuring a timeless experience that feels both familiar and safe. It is more than just a plot of land; it is a repository of memories for families and a daily ritual for the neighborhood. For those who value consistency, heritage, and a strong sense of place, this Cherry Hill Township staple remains the gold standard.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://www.campbowwow.com/cherry-hill/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/challenge-grove-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Challenge Grove Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 6:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Cherry Hill Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Serious about your pup&#x27;s fitness and focus? Challenge Grove Park in [Cherry Hill Township](/cities/cherry-hill-township-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 4.7 stars by a community of 357 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of &quot;constructive play.&quot; It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\n\nThe layout at Challenge Grove Park is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://www.camdencounty.com/service/parks/challenge-grove-park/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/cooper-river-dog-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Cooper River Dog Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 6:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Cherry Hill Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Cooper River Dog Park has become a favorite among the area residents.  What makes this dog facility special is its professional, reliable, spacious. The staff&#x27;s dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. professional and reliable service Located in a safe area, This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. </p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/croft-farm\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Croft Farm</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 9:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Cherry Hill Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Serious about your pup&#x27;s fitness and focus? Croft Farm in [Cherry Hill Township](/cities/cherry-hill-township-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 4.7 stars by a community of 32 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of &quot;constructive play.&quot; It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\n\nThe layout at Croft Farm is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](http://www.chnj.gov/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/croft-farm-dog-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Croft Farm Dog Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Hours vary by season</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Cherry Hill Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Croft Farm Dog Park has become a favorite among the area residents.  What makes this dog facility special is its friendly, caring, spacious. The staff&#x27;s dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. staff is very friendly and caring This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. </p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/dog-training-by-bruce\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Dog Training By Bruce</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>0</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 9:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Cherry Hill Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Dog Training By Bruce is a dog facility located in the area.  What makes this dog facility special is its convenient, spacious, great. convenient location with good parking Located in a convenient area, This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (609) 828-9985. Visit their website at https://dogtrainingbybruce.com/ to learn more about their services and pricing.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/dogtopia-of-cherry-hill\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Dogtopia of Cherry Hill</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 7:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Cherry Hill Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">If you&#x27;re looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [Cherry Hill Township](/cities/cherry-hill-township-nj), look no further than Dogtopia of Cherry Hill. This vibrant community destination has earned a reputation as the &quot;place to be&quot; for local pet parents who want more than just a walk—they want a meetup. Boasting a solid 4.5-star rating from 44 reviews, the park radiates a welcoming energy where tails never stop wagging and neighbors become friends. Whether you&#x27;re there for a quick playdate or a long afternoon of socializing, the atmosphere is always buzzing with positivity.\n\nAt Dogtopia of Cherry Hill, the focus is on connection. The layout encourages interaction, making it easy for pups to find playmates while owners chat on the sidelines. It’s not just a facility; it’s a social pillar of the Cherry Hill Township scene, offering a safe, clean, and joyous environment where every visitor feels like a VIP. For a fun, friendly, and community-centered experience, this spot is a local favorite.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://www.dogtopia.com/cherryhill) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a></div><div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:2rem\"><button class=\"hero-cta primary\" style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;cursor:pointer\"><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down\"></i>Show More (<!-- -->13<!-- --> more)</button></div></div></div></section><section id=\"nearby-cities\" class=\"nearby-cities-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Explore the region</span><h2>Dog parks near <!-- -->Cherry Hill Township</h2><p>Worth the drive? Check out top-rated indoor parks in neighboring cities.</p></div><div class=\"nearby-cities-grid\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2rem\"><a class=\"nearby-city-card\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:white;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;transition:transform 0.2s\" href=\"/cities/jersey-city\"><div class=\"nearby-city-image\" style=\"position:relative;height:180px;background-color:#f1f5f9\"><img alt=\"Dog parks in Jersey City, NJ\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/jersey-city/hero.webp\"/></div><div class=\"nearby-city-content\" style=\"padding:1rem\"><h3 style=\"font-size:1.125rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:0.5rem;color:#0f172a\">Jersey City</h3><p style=\"font-size:0.875rem;color:#64748b\">47<!-- --> parks · <!-- -->4.5<!-- --> avg rating</p></div></a><a class=\"nearby-city-card\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:white;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;transition:transform 