 with designer Kuranda® bedding and specialized DogTV to keep guests calm and entertained in a peaceful, climate-controlled setting.\n\nThe daycare program at K9 Resorts Cherry Hill is exceptionally structured, providing a healthy balance of social interaction and vigorous exercise. Canine guests enjoy supervised play in expansive outdoor yards and climate-controlled indoor parks, with groups carefully divided by size and temperament. For dogs that require more direct human connection, the hotel provides 'Individualized Daycare' sessions that include one-on-one playtime with the highly trained and certified staff. Luxury 'pampering' upgrades are a hallmark of the experience, including in-house made gourmet doggie ice cream, premium Blue Buffalo meals, and professional bathing services in their dedicated wash spa. The facility also offers appreciation discounts for military members and first responders, reinforcing its deep roots in the local community. With a verified reputation for exceptional service and a staff of genuine animal lovers, K9 Resorts Cherry Hill delivers a high-touch, premium care solution. Whether your pup is joining for a day of spirited social play or an extended luxury holiday, the team treats every guest with the expert logic and individualized affection they deserve.34:T462,For years, Pawllywood Grooming Cherry Hill has served as a steadfast anchor of the [Cherry Hill Township](/cities/cherry-hill-township-nj) community, earning its place as a beloved local institution. With a history of serving generations of tail-waggers, this location carries a sense of established trust and neighborhood pride that you can't manufacture. Documented by 200 reviews and a 4.7-star legacy, it stands as a testament to the town's enduring commitment to its animal residents.\n\nStepping into Pawllywood Grooming Cherry Hill feels like visiting an old friend. The facility balances traditional park values with modern maintenance standards, ensuring a timeless experie